1
00:00:01,341 --> 00:00:04,022
This is the main page of the e-learning platform.

2
00:00:05,032 --> 00:00:11,232
You can navigate, and get more information about using the main menu, or the other options provided.

3
00:00:15,062 --> 00:00:21,926
The two year course e-learning program is an academic online program, based on the highest educational standards

4
00:00:22,669 --> 00:00:25,243
according to the principles of Samuel Hahnemann.

5
00:00:26,361 --> 00:00:31,947
You can find more information about the program the curriculum, the conditions and the fees

6
00:00:32,019 --> 00:00:35,315
by clicking on the corresponding sub-menu items.

7
00:00:37,275 --> 00:00:42,443
Here you can see the available 2-year course, e-learning versions.

8
00:00:47,883 --> 00:00:55,735
By clicking the view button you can get more information such as the course language, the total videos and the provided facilities.

9
00:00:56,304 --> 00:01:01,192
You can also get a 10-day free trial by clicking the "Get Free Trial"  button.

10
00:01:02,040 --> 00:01:08,760
For more information about the free trial, please visit the corresponding link on the main page.

11
00:01:09,353 --> 00:01:12,433
Now let's register for a free trial.

12
00:01:16,289 --> 00:01:21,576
We are redirected to the registration page, we enter our personal data.

13
00:01:26,767 --> 00:01:30,527
You should also read the instructions underneath each box.

14
00:01:52,556 --> 00:01:56,636
The 2-year course is selected as default, in this drop-down list.

15
00:02:04,162 --> 00:02:07,898
Now we must select language, from the available options.

16
00:02:14,315 --> 00:02:16,795
Selecting language is actually for a later use,

17
00:02:16,969 --> 00:02:20,961
when you have purchased the course, you are registered to the corresponding course

18
00:02:21,206 --> 00:02:25,462
and the provided content is in the language you have chosen in this step.

19
00:02:26,497 --> 00:02:28,736
We continue with the registration.

20
00:02:30,533 --> 00:02:34,221
And now we click the "Create new account"  button to finish.

21
00:02:38,488 --> 00:02:41,200
The registration process has finished.

22
00:02:41,678 --> 00:02:45,853
An e-mail has been sent to the e-mail account we have entered.

23
00:02:46,185 --> 00:02:51,652
You should open this e-mail and click on the link provided, to confirm your registration.

24
00:02:52,535 --> 00:02:58,463
A new free trial group begins every Friday, and you will be notified by e-mail from the Academy.

25
00:03:00,995 --> 00:03:05,483
Now let's see how to register for a post-graduate course.

26
00:03:09,525 --> 00:03:14,621
From this menu item we can see the post-graduate courses of the Academy.

27
00:03:18,198 --> 00:03:22,806
In this page we can see the available post-graduate courses.

28
00:03:39,425 --> 00:03:43,848
In the same way, we can get more information by clicking the view button.

29
00:03:44,155 --> 00:03:50,795
If you already have an account on the e-learning platform, and want to register to a post-graduate course,

30
00:03:51,067 --> 00:03:55,183
just send and e-mail to the Academy, that you want to register to this specific course.

31
00:03:56,572 --> 00:04:00,675
If you don't have an account yet click the "Register now" button.

32
00:04:04,923 --> 00:04:07,882
We are redirected to the registration page.

33
00:04:17,581 --> 00:04:26,673
We enter our personal data as we showed before, and select the post-graduate levels of health course and language from the available options.

34
00:04:43,595 --> 00:04:47,427
We continue with the form, and click the "Create new account" button.

35
00:04:48,366 --> 00:04:56,317
Open the e-mail to confirm your registration and another e-mail will be sent to you from the academy to process with the payment.

36
00:04:57,061 --> 00:05:01,876
Once the payment is complete you will have access to the course.

